<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/28044664" target="_blank" data-id="3400516" data-za-element-name="Title">
月薪10-12k的前端人员应该具备怎样一种技术水平？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/28044664/answer/39393092">
