<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/21445727" target="_blank" data-id="758987" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么 Web 前端开发不抛弃 HTML 和 CSS，用纯 JavaScript 开发？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/21445727/answer/18399257">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="2509453">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="18399257"> -->

